sequenceDiagram
  participant Stu as Student
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant BE as Backend
  participant DB as DB
  Stu->>FE: Start Exam
  FE->>BE: POST /exams/:id/start
  BE->>DB: Create attempt
  DB-->>BE: Attempt id
  BE-->>FE: Attempt token/id
  loop every 10s
    FE->>BE: POST /attempts/:id/save (answers)
    BE->>DB: Upsert answers
  end
  Stu->>FE: Submit
  FE->>BE: POST /attempts/:id/submit
  BE->>DB: Evaluate & store result
  BE-->>FE: Result summary
